events.title: "New Leadership Takes Flight: Group Captain C. E. St. J. Beamish Assumes Command of Wing on June 9, 1945"
events.description: 312. On 9th June, 1945, the Wing passed to the Command of Group Captain C. E. St. J. Beamish, D.F.C. .
events.summary: 6 September:  On 9th June, 1945, the Wing passed to the Command of Group Captain C. E. St. J. Beamish, D.F.C. Beamsish . The Wing is now based in St. Mary's Hospital, London, and is based in the United States .
